LineGraph version 0.01
==============================

    Tk::LineGraph - A Tk widget that will do a line graph of data setoed in a LineGraphDataset.

    WARNING: This is a beta version.  Tested on RedHat 7 Linux and Windows/XP.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Tk, Tk::LineGraphDataset

